list.abstract: 《BIRTH》，是日本Johnnys人气偶像团体KAT-TUN的第十七张单曲。这首新曲是为龟梨和也主演的热播日剧《妖怪人间贝姆》演唱的片尾曲。
《Birth》是日本歌手喜多村英梨演唱的歌曲。由山口朗彦作词、作曲，收录在喜多村英梨2013年8月发行的专辑《Birth(通常盤)》中。在Orcon周间最高位为20位。

yingyinNormal.en: Suez? Birth? It's a big night for canals.
yingyinNormal.zh: 苏伊士？出生日？运河今夜逢吉时。

yingyinNormal.en: It was hilarious. Now, how can a birth be hilarious, you ask? A teenage doctor helps.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我出生时可搞笑了。也许你会问，出生时有什么搞笑的。当时帮忙的医生很年轻。

yingyinNormal.en: Our first birthday. Okay, birth. So then, we celebrate our birth every year. What's next?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的第一个生日。好的，首先是出生。然后，我们每年都庆祝生日，还有什么？

yingyinNormal.en: I actually needed to talk to you before the birth. Okay, what's up?
yingyinNormal.zh: 在孩子出生前我得跟你谈一谈。好吧，什么事？

yingyinNormal.en: The Hashshashin were crushed by my uncle Hülegü long before my birth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哈沙辛人早在我出生之前就被我叔叔旭烈兀消灭了。

yingyinNormal.en: Farkle? Birth. Okay, let's go with that because it's not what you said.
yingyinNormal.zh: 法尔科？出生。好的，这个回答可以，起码跟你们的不一样。

yingyinNormal.en: I just don't look ordinary when I'm doing these things. Not even my birth was ordinary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 只是我做事的样子和普通小孩不一样。我出生时的情况也跟他们不一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, who were they? I don't know. I don't know if I'll ever know. There aren't birth records.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那么，他们是谁？我不知道，我不知道我能否知道。那里没有出生记录。

yingyinNormal.en: Then what's this? What's that date? Is that a birth day? Is that a death day? I don't know yet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是什么？这个日期代表什么？出生日期？还是死亡日期？目前还不清楚。

yingyinNormal.en: At Christmas, our attention is drawn to the birth of a baby some two thousand years ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 每当圣诞时节，两千多年前出生的一个小男孩总是会引起我们的关注(指耶稣的诞生)。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, we get some mahogany boxes and carve everyone's names in them and inside is everyone's individual birth stone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 用一个红木箱，刻上每个人的名字，在里面放着每个人的出生石。

yingyinNormal.en: Tara, he has birth defects. I know it feels like he's healthy, but he'll be in pain when he's born, and he won't survive.
yingyinNormal.zh: 塔拉，他有先天缺陷。我知道你觉得他很健康，但他出生后会很痛苦，而且他活不下来。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. It tells us that you participate in the mass cultural delusion that the sun's apparent position relative to arbitrarily defined constellations at the time of your birth, somehow affects your personality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没错，我们可以了解到，你有群众性文化妄想，就是指你出生时相对于任意确定星座的太阳的视位置，可能会决定你的性格。

yingyinNormal.en: The birth not just of a baby in a manger, but of a message that has changed the world to reach out to the sick, the hungry, the troubled and above all else to love one another as we would be loved ourselves.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这不仅是在马槽中一个婴儿的出生，而且是一个已经改变世界启示的诞生，向患病，饥饿，患难的人伸出援手，除此最重要的是爱其他的人，正如我们会爱我们自己一样。

yingyinNormal.en: Image number six: woman giving birth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 画面6: 妇女生产。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. And so the miracle of birth begins.
yingyinNormal.zh: 生命的奇迹开始了…

yingyinNormal.en: We must put aside all talks of death, and focus on birth. The birth of a new age.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不要谈论死亡，而要关注诞生。新时代的诞生。

yingyinNormal.en: Actually, giving birth to three babies isn't that different from giving birth to one.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实生三个跟生一个一样。

yingyinNormal.en: You're Ned's son? Yeah. Yeah. Ned gave birth to me. Well, he didn't give birth. You know what I meant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是内德的儿子? 嗯嗯，内德生了我，呃，不是他生的，你懂我意思吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, honey, maybe you can talk to somebody who's had a baby. Like your mom? My mom never gave birth. Oh. But my birth mom did.
yingyinNormal.zh: 或许和生过小孩的人讨论一下，好比你母亲。我妈才没生过小孩呢，不过我的生母有。

examination_example.sentence: Before the <highlight>birth</highlight> of proper dentistry, mouths were often in a shocking state of hygiene.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在真正的牙科诞生之前，人们的口腔经常处于非常糟糕的卫生状态。

examination_example.sentence: By the date of his <highlight>birth</highlight> Europe was witnessing the passing of the religious drama, and the creation of new forms under the incentive of classical tragedy and comedy.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 到他出生之日，欧洲正在见证宗教戏剧的消亡，以及在古典悲剧和喜剧的推动下新的戏剧形式的诞生。

examination_example.sentence: Yet two years before Dicken's <highlight>birth</highlight>, his mother's father was caught stealing and fled to Europe, never to return.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然而，在狄更斯出生前两年，他的爷爷被抓到偷窃并逃往欧洲，再也没有回来。
